Cioss 6637 Sonogno Switzerland


1131
01:30:42.113 --> 01:30:43.571
<i>Dear Mom,</i>

1132
01:30:44.030 --> 01:30:47.363
<i>I don't know if you're still in Madrid
and living in the same house,</i>


1133
01:30:47.905 --> 01:30:50.696
<i>but I have no other address for you.</i>

1134
01:30:51.988 --> 01:30:53.405
<i>I have three children.</i>

1135
01:30:54.571 --> 01:30:55.654
<i>Xoan,</i>

1136
01:30:55.988 --> 01:30:57.489
<i>the eldest,</i>

1137
01:30:57.654 --> 01:30:59.405
<i>was only nine years old</i>

1138
01:30:59.654 --> 01:31:02.030
<i>when he drowned in a river.</i>

1139
01:31:02.405 --> 01:31:04.654
<i>And I am insane with grief.</i>

1140
01:31:06.613 --> 01:31:08.322
<i>In these moments,</i>

1141
01:31:09.155 --> 01:31:11.571
<i>the worst in my entire life,</i>

1142
01:31:12.280 --> 01:31:13.654
<i>I'm thinking of you.</i>

1143
01:31:15.071 --> 01:31:18.571
<i>Now I understand what you must
have suffered when I disappeared.</i>


1144
01:31:19.863 --> 01:31:21.696
<i>I couldn't imagine it.</i>

1145
01:31:22.489 --> 01:31:25.821
<i>No one who hasn't
suffered it can imagine it.</i>


1146
01:31:28.363 --> 01:31:30.654
I'm not going to ask
her for an explanation.


1147
01:31:33.489 --> 01:31:35.238
I just want to be with her.

1148
01:31:37.280 --> 01:31:39.072
But she didn't invite me to come...

1149
01:31:40.405 --> 01:31:42.405
After 13 years she didn't dare,

1150
01:31:42.654 --> 01:31:44.780
but she put her return address.